            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "from my"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "breast is"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "heard."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then the Spirit, in like manner,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "Em",
              "text": "helps me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Praying"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "in my"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "weakness"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "unto"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "God."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, my prayer is not for deeper suffering,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But that from each trial I’d be free."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let the cup of bitterness be taken;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet, Thy will, not mine, dear Lord, must be."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Even now, though trials sore surround me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Still within my heart there is a peace,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the love of God outpoured within me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Floods my heart and bids my doubting cease."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Blest assurance! God has fully ordered"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every matter by His sovereign hand;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every person (though we see so dimly),"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every thing’s according to His plan."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every trial is but the Father’s answer"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To the groaning of the Spirit’s prayer;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "May He gain in every tribulation,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Until we Christ’s glory fully share."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How could God from all His dealings spare us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "After He spared not His only Son?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Could the Potter’s hand upon the vessel"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever leave the shaping work undone?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the center of God’s heart’s desire"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is that many brethren we will be"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Unto Christ, His precious First-begotten,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to Him, conformed we’ll fully be."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Heirs of God! Joint-heirs with our Lord Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What a hope of glory this for us!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though the suff’rings presently seem grievous,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Greater far the glory then for us!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yea, in all these things we more than conquer,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through the One whose love has us possessed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Soon the day for which waits all creation,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When the sons of God are manifest!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
  ],
